
The current McSPI testsuite verify data transmission with different
configuration options in McSPI channel 4. In order to execute the
test scenarios your local Kernel must contain the following patch:

PATCH: mcspi_test.patch

This testsuites is executed with McSPI channel 4 in loopback mode,
so the following lines must shorted:

McSPI4_SOMI <---->  McSPI4_SIMO

In 44xx SDP platform these lines correspond to the following resistors:

R482 <-----> R487

